@host = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@person = Julian
@messageID = 157312
@phrase = n
@since = 2026-04-01
@until = 2026-04-28

### Health
GET {{host}}/healthz

### Count rows in Apple's message table
GET {{host}}/api/messages/count

### Local index status
GET {{host}}/api/index/status

### Local index text-source stats
GET {{host}}/api/index/stats

### Sync new messages into the local plain-text index
POST {{host}}/api/index/sync

### Rebuild the local plain-text index from scratch
POST {{host}}/api/index/rebuild

### Search messages with a person by contact name, phone, email, or chat name
GET {{host}}/api/messages/search?person={{person}}&limit=50

### Search messages containing a word or phrase
GET {{host}}/api/messages/search?phrase={{phrase}}&limit=50

### Ranked weighted keyword search
GET {{host}}/api/messages/search?phrase=school%20pickup%20time&mode=ranked&limit=50

### Exact phrase search
GET {{host}}/api/messages/search?phrase=school%20pickup%20time&mode=exact&limit=50

### Search messages with a person containing a word or phrase
GET {{host}}/api/messages/search?person={{person}}&phrase={{phrase}}&limit=50

### Search messages with a person during a relative timeframe
GET {{host}}/api/messages/search?person={{person}}&timeframe=last_week&limit=50

### Search messages containing a phrase between two dates
GET {{host}}/api/messages/search?phrase={{phrase}}&since={{since}}&until={{until}}&limit=50

### Browse all indexed messages between two dates
GET {{host}}/api/messages/search?since={{since}}&until={{until}}&limit=50

### Fetch surrounding conversation context for one message
GET {{host}}/api/messages/{{messageID}}/context?before=10&after=10
